  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dd3, \u0db1\u0dcf\u0db8\u0dbd\u0dca, \u0db8\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf, \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dad, \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d87\u0db8\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db0\u0dd4\u0dbb \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Basil requests the President to give ministerial posts to Johnny, Namal, Mahindananda, Rohitha, Pavitra and others.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A spokesman for the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna told 'Ada' that there is now a belief in the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna that the appointment of the new cabinet will be delayed.",
        "He pointed out that the President's approval of the party's national organizer Mr. Basil Rajapaksa's request to get cabinet ministerships including the district leaders of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna has been temporarily postponed.",
        "Also, the spokesman pointed out that the protest raised by the Samagijana Balawega and the MPs associated with it was the reason for this and said that the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna internally believes that the President will work to find a solution for it.",
        "Mr. Basil Rajapaksa has asked the President to give ministerial posts in the new cabinet to be appointed to a group of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna members including Johnston Fernando, Namal Rajapaksa, Mahindananda Aluthgamage, Rohitha Abeygunawardena, Pavithradevi Vanniarachchi, and together with the Saagi Jana Balawega A group of MPs protested."
      ],
